<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink50-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">maṉaiyiṉ nīṅkip parattaiyiṭattup paṉṉāḷ taṅkivanta talaimakaṟkut tōḻi colliyatu.</p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink50">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>tuṇaiyōr celvamum yāmum varuntutum</l>
<l>vañci yōṅkiya yāṇa rūra</l>
<l>tañca maruḷāy nīyēniṉ</l>
<l>neñcam peṟṟa vivaḷumā raḻumē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
 
<l> O man from a fertile village </l> 
<l rend="indent2"> where the Mahua trees have grown tall! </l> 
<l> We are suffering – my wealth of girlfriends and I. </l> 
<l> You have been a trifle inconsiderate. </l> 
<l> The girl who won </l> 
<l> your heart – </l> 
<l> she too is weeping. </l> 



</lg>
